Class NewickTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ecosim.NewickTreeNode

  • public class NewickTreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
    A Newick tree node potentially contains a name, a parent node, a distance from the parent node, and a list of all child nodes.
    Author:
    Andrew Warner & Jason Wood
